---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="RoKGuides privacy policy: information on cookie usage, third-party advertising services, and data collection."
  lang="en"
  alternatePath="/gizlilik-politikasi"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-foreground">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:text-accent-purple-light mt-8 max-w-none">
      <p>
        At RoKGuides, we care about our visitors' privacy. This page explains what data is collected while using
        our site and how it is used.
      </p>
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Our site may use Google Analytics cookies to improve user experience and analyze traffic.
      </p>
      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        Our site may display third-party ads through Google AdSense. Google may use cookies to serve
        interest-based ads. You can learn more about Google's advertising policies in Google's own privacy policy.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about our privacy policy, you can use our <a href="/en/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
